  "detailed_description": "Dive into a dark and hostile world where death is just the beginning. <strong>Forsaken Ones</strong> is a boss rush game with soulslike action that challenges players to face epic bosses in brutal combat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/04a8e3864a07169468b33c153f34893b.poster.avif?t=1743109584\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/04a8e3864a07169468b33c153f34893b.webm?t=1743109584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/04a8e3864a07169468b33c153f34893b.mp4?t=1743109584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Third-person Combat:</strong> Experience soulslike mechanics.<br></li><li><strong>Boss Rush:</strong> Step through a portal into a gauntlet of epic and unique boss encounters.<br></li><li><strong>Diverse Playstyles:</strong> Choose from a roster of playable characters, each with unique abilities to suit your style.<br></li><li><strong>Scalable Healing:</strong> Increase your healing pool after defeating a boss, but it resets upon character death.<br></li><li><strong>Immersive Soundtrack:</strong> Each boss boasts a unique musical theme.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/cc300705ebc8802072b6046f08ede74b.poster.avif?t=1743109584\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/cc300705ebc8802072b6046f08ede74b.webm?t=1743109584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094650/extras/cc300705ebc8802072b6046f08ede74b.mp4?t=1743109584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
